data.description: ***VA buyers take note of the unique opportunity to explore an assumable VA loan with a low 2.5% fixed interest rate.*** Discover the perfect blend of comfort and style in this sought-after single-story residence. Boasting a 3-bed, 2-bath layout with contemporary finishes, this property exudes modern charm. Revel in the fresh ambiance created by new paint, wood-look tile flooring, and expansive dual-paned windows, offering a luminous and spacious atmosphere. The well-appointed kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, a double oven, and a chic glass tile backsplash. Entertain seamlessly as the generous dining area flows into a living room adorned with a captivating brick fireplace. Retreat to the primary bedroom, complete with a remodeled bathroom showcasing a shower bench and exquisite tile craftsmanship. Both oversized secondary bedrooms share a guest bathroom with a spacious vanity. Step outside to a vast, landscaped backyard with a covered patio, firepit, and potential for a pool, sports court and so much more on this over 10,000 square foot lot. Enjoy added comfort with ceiling fans in great room and all bedrooms as well as a new air conditioner. This property includes an attached 2-car garage with block wall fencing with RV access.
